Mix up 8 tbsp of liquid smoke with 3/4 cup of Hunt's original barbecue
sauce.  Boil the ribs until the bone is beginning to show, then  dip the
ribs in the barbecue sauce mix, Lay the ribs under the electric broiler
for 3 minutes per side.  Remove, paint on the remainder of the sauce and
enjoy.

